<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Scarpa</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-16 07:30:59</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, uh....back to the quest.  I finally found her.  She is about 50 feet away and 100 feet south of Guk entrance.  Kill the Troll Slayer, and the named that hang around there.  All green so no worries.  When Lynuga spawns, hail her, give her a ruby, pray.  If you don't keep hailing her, she disappears.  She spawns twice in a row, then not for 5 days, so if you don't catch her, you're out of luck.  She is KoS to light races, so make a mule.  When I tried it, someone gave her a ruby before I got a chance and got the hoop.  47 rubies later, no hoop.</font></td></tr></table>
